quran[62]{c,v,t}:
  37,83,“Ndipo ndithu m’gulu lake (la Nuh) muli Ibrahim
  37,84,“Kumbuka pamene adadza kwa Mbuye wake ndi mtima wabwino (wogonjera malamulo)
  37,85,"“Pomwe adanena kwa bambo wake ndi anthu ake: “Mukupembedza chiyani?”"
  37,86,"““Ha! Milungu yopeka kusiya Allah, ndi imene mukuifuna?”"
  37,87,““Kodi maganizo anu ngotani pa Mbuye wa zolengedwa zonse?”
  37,88,“Ndipo adayang’ana nyenyezi mozama
  37,89,"“Ndipo adanena: “Ine ndine wodwala!”"
  37,90,“Choncho iwo adatembenuka ndi kumsiya
  37,91,"“(Ibrahim) adapita mozemba ku mafano awo, ndipo adawauza (mwachipongwe:) “Bwanji simukudya (chakudya chomwe chaikidwa patsogolo panupo)?”"
  37,92,““Bwanji simukuyankhula?”
  37,93,“Atatero adawatembenukira ndi kuwamenya (mwamphamvu) ndi dzanja lamanja
  37,94,“(Pamene adamva eni mafanowo) adadza kwa iye akuthamanga
  37,95,"“Anati: “Kodi mukupembedza (miyala) imene mwasema?”"
  37,96,““Chikhalirecho Allah ndiye adakulengani ndi zimene mukuchita!”
  37,97,"“Iwo adati: “Mmangireni ng’anjo, ndipo mponyeni m’motowo.”"
  37,98,"“Adafuna kumchita chiwembu (kuti amuphe ndi moto), koma tidawachita kukhala onyozeka"
  37,99,"“Ndipo (Ibrahim) adati: “Ndithu ine ndikupita kwa Mbuye wanga, Iye andiongolera.”"
  37,100,““E Mbuye wanga! Ndipatseni mwana yemwe adzakhale (mmodzi) mwa olungama!”
  37,101,"“Ndipo tidamuuza nkhani yabwino ya mwana wofatsa, (mwanayo ndi Ismaila)"
  37,102,"“Ndipo (adabadwa ndi kuyamba kukula.) Pamene adakwana nsinkhu woyenda pamodzi ndi tate wake pochitachita za m’dziko (Ibrahim adayesedwa mayeso kupyolera m’maloto omwe adalota). Adati: “E mwana wanga! Ine kutulo ndikuona maloto (owona ochokera kwa Allah omwe akundilamula) kuti ndikuzinge (monga nsembe yopereka kwa Allah). Nanga ukuti bwanji?” (Mwana wabwino) adanena: “Bambo wanga! Kwaniritsani chimene mukulamulidwa. Ngati Allah afuna, mundipeza ndili mmodzi mwa opirira.”"
  37,103,"“Pamene adagonjera onse awiri (chofuna cha Allah), ndipo (Ibrahim) adam’goneka chakumphumi (ndipo adatsimikiza kumupha)"
  37,104,"“Ndipo tidamuitana: “E iwe Ibrahim!”"
  37,105,““Ndithu wavomereza maloto! (Choncho usamuphe mwana wakoyo).” Umo ndi momwe timawalipirira ochita zabwino
  37,106,“Ndithu amenewa ndimayeso oonekera
  37,107,“Ndipo tidampulumutsa pompatsa nyama yayikulu (yoti apereke nsembe)
  37,108,“Ndipo tidamsiira (mbiri yabwino) kwa anthu ena (amene adadza pambuyo pake)
  37,109,“Mtendere ukhale pa Ibrahim
  37,110,“M’menemo ndi mornwe timawalipirira ochita zabwino
  37,111,“Ndithu iye adali mmodzi mwa akapolo Athu okhulupirira
  37,112,“Ndiponso tidamuuza nkhani yabwino (yoti akhala ndi mwana wotchedwa) Isihaqa; mneneri; wam’gulu la olungama
  37,113,“Ndipo tidamdalitsa iye ndi (mwana wake) Isihaqa; ndipo m’mbumba ya awiriwa mudapezeka abwino ndi odzichitira zoipa owonekera
  37,114,"“Ndipo ndithu tidawachitira zabwino Mûsa ndi Haruna, (powapatsa uneneri ndi madalitso ambiri)"
  37,115,“Ndipo tidawapulumutsa (awiriwa) ndi anthu awo ku vuto lalikulu
  37,116,"“Ndipo tidawathangata (powagonjetsera adani awo), ndipo iwo adali opambana"
  37,117,“Ndipo tidawapatsa (Mûsa ndi Haruna) buku losonyeza poyera (malamulo)
  37,118,“Ndipo tidawaongolera ku njira yolunjika
  37,119,“Ndiponso tidawasiira (mbiri yabwino) kwa anthu ena (amene adadza pambuyo pawo)
  37,120,“Mtendere ukhale pa Mûsa ndi Haruna
  37,121,“Ndithu umu ndi momwe Ife timawalipirira ochita zabwino
  37,122,“Ndithu awiriwa adali m’gulu la akapoio Athu okhulupirira
  37,123,“Ndipo ndithu Iliyasa ndi mmodzi wa atumiki
  37,124,"“(Kumbuka) pamene adanena kwa anthu ake: “Bwanji simuopa (Allah)?”"
  37,125,““Mukupembedza (fano lotchedwa) Ba’la ndi kusiya (kupembedza) Wabwino zedi mwa olenga onse.”
  37,126,"““Allah, Mbuye wanu ndi Mbuye wa makolo anu akale?”"
  37,127,“Koma adamtsutsa; ndithu iwo adzaonekera (ku Moto)
  37,128,“Kupatula akapolo a Allah amene ayeretsedwa (ndi Allah)
  37,129,“Ndipo tidamsiira (mbiri yabwino) kwa anthu ena (amene adadza pambuyo pake)
  37,130,“Mtendere ukhale pa Iliyasiin
  37,131,“Ndithu umo ndi mmene Ife timawalipirira ochita zabwino
  37,132,“Ndithu iye ndimmodzi mwa akapolo Athu okhulupirira
  37,133,“Ndithu Luti ndi mmodzi wa atumiki
  37,134,“(Kumbuka) pamene tidampulumutsa iye ndi anthu ake onse
  37,135,“Kupatula nkhalamba yachikazi; idali mwa otsalira
  37,136,“Kenako tidawaononga enawo (omwe adali oipa)
  37,137,“Ndithu inu (a mumzinda wa Makka) mumadutsa pa malo pawopo m’mawa
  37,138,“Ndi usiku. Kodi bwanji simuzindikira
  37,139,“Ndithu Yunusu ndi mmodzi wa atumiki
  37,140,“(Kumbuka) pamene adathawira m’chombo chodzazidwa (ndi katundu)
  37,141,"“Choncho adachita mayere, ndipo adali m’gulu la omgwera (mayerewo)"
  37,142,“Choncho nsomba idammeza uku ali wodzudzulidwa
  37,143,“Kukadapanda kuti iye adali m’modzi mwa otamanda ndi kulemekeza Allah
  37,144,“Akadakhala m’mimba mwake mpaka tsiku loukitsidwa (zolengedwa ku imfa)